{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deceit 2 is an online social deduction horror game. Inspire fear as the Infected, play detective as the Innocent, or create mayhem as the Cursed. Trapped with friends and strangers: who can you trust to help you escape? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE TEAMS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/Steam_Storepage_InnocentBanner.png?t=1736435241\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE INNOCENT: SURVIVE AND ESCAPE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stay alive and outwit the Infected or meet a grim fate. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete tasks around the map to bring you closer to obtaining the escape key.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Investigate suspicious activity and keep an eye on your fellow players\u2019 actions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/Steam_Storepage_InfectedBanner__1_.png?t=1736435241\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE INFECTED: DECEIVE AND KILL</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Transform and execute other players to whittle down the ranks of the Innocent.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover Mutation perks and give you even stronger powers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn the trust of your team: blend in and wait for the moment to strike.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/Cursed.png?t=1736435241\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE CURSED: CONFUSION AND MAYHEM</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deceive Infected and Innocents alike and avoid suspicion. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become a true agent of chaos, and exploit your curse to win the game your way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock ever stronger curses as you outwit friend and foe.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064870/extras/Steam_Storepage_MasteryBanner_Gold.png?t=1736435241\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MASTER THE RITUAL</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Climb the ranks of Ascension to become a master of Deceit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new items to help you escape, and unleash new Mutations to give you an edge as the Infected.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expand your wardrobe with epic character and item cosmetics.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Freedom?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2064870/d9b13594691eb7d3a1ef34d034a2e0c6ed1934bf.jpg"},{"name":"Extermination","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2064870/00d2854e67e1be2cde84399989e84bed3db4ecdb.jpg"},{"name":"Mutant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2064870/46bbd49a7f3e8bc72f086232cf69528ddee33e2e.jpg"},{"name":"Shame On Me","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2064870/3a91b39111e6795d2057a1982a7213d5be657322.jpg"},{"name":"Fool Me Once","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2064870/6894b9678b791d9777788deb3a2618478fe723b2.jpg"},{"name":"Shame On You","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2064870/fc824223fb4548513ff8a62e54389c02b3f150f2.jpg"},{"name":"Swagged Out","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2064870/b75dae3766b1bc4bf337d350152ab4744726248f.jpg"},{"name":"Escape Artist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2064870/97eca113c9b6c9d81bb59d8bdea81b4fca92827c.jpg"},{"name":"Blood Lust","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.c